      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and<strong> red wine vinegar</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>honey chipotle dressing</strong></p>",
