    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong>,<strong> drained sweetcorn</strong> and<strong> crispy tortilla strips </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>honey chipotle dressing </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)<strong> </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>taco salad</strong></p>",
